graph TD
    CAP["CAP Theorem"] --> C["Consistency<br/>All nodes see same data"]
    CAP --> A["Availability<br/>Always responds"]
    CAP --> P["Partition Tolerance<br/>Survives network splits"]
    P --> CP["CP Systems<br/>HBase · Zookeeper · etcd"]
    P --> AP["AP Systems<br/>Cassandra · CouchDB · Dynamo"]
